        Execute a SQL file bundled with the plugin
        Parameters:
        filename - full file name, including extension, in resources/sql folder
        replacementMap - {{key}} in the file will be replaced by value. Ignored if null. NOTE: sql injection will happen
        cls - class of desired object
        parameters - JDBC's positional parametrized query.
